title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Invetero Coquette D10 Pursuit
content:
The Invetero Coquette D10 Pursuit is a top-of-the-line law enforcement vehicle that doesn’t just level the playing field — it blurs it entirely. It’ll be hard to tell if the sirens are yours or a nearby LSPD officer trying to apprehend you.

Now available from Warstock Cache & Carry. Complete the Slush Fund mission from The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid as leader to unlock for purchase. Successfully completing 10 Dispatch Work assignments will unlock the Trade Price.
